name: dï⊕ηε
description:
dï⊕ηε is based one of Saturn's moons of the same name. dione has some interesting patterns on it's surface, which when textured in the right way, leads to an almost jewel-like feel. 

this is part of my 𝐜𝐞𝐥𝐞𝐬𝐭𝐢𝐚𝐥 𝐯𝐢𝐬𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬 collection. it combines my love for space & astronomy, with an abstract monochrome art style. every artwork is a satisfying infinite loop of motion.
